### Task API — manual test requests
### Click "Send Request" above any HTTP method line to test it.

### ============== HEALTH ==============

### Liveness
GET http://localhost:3000/health

### Readiness
GET http://localhost:3000/health/ready

### ============== ROOT ==============

### API info
GET http://localhost:3000/

### ============== TASKS — READ ==============

### List all tasks
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/tasks

### List only completed tasks
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/tasks?completed=true

### List only pending tasks
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/tasks?completed=false

### List by priority high
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/tasks?priority=high

### List by tag welcome
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/tasks?tag=welcome

### Get a single task by id
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/tasks/1

### Get stats
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/tasks/stats

### ============== TASKS — CREATE ==============

### Create — minimum required (just title)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/v1/tasks
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Learn Docker basics"
}

### Create — full payload with priority, due date, tags
POST http://localhost:3000/api/v1/tasks
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Deploy first containerized app",
  "priority": "high",
  "dueDate": "2026-05-25T18:00:00Z",
  "tags": ["docker", "learning", "devops"]
}

### Create — overdue task
POST http://localhost:3000/api/v1/tasks
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "This is overdue",
  "priority": "high",
  "dueDate": "2024-01-01T00:00:00Z"
}

### ============== TASKS — UPDATE ==============

### Mark task as completed
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/v1/tasks/3
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "completed": true
}

### Multi-field update
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/v1/tasks/3
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Updated title",
  "priority": "medium",
  "dueDate": "2026-06-01T00:00:00Z",
  "completed": false
}

### ============== TASKS — DELETE ==============

### Delete a task
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/v1/tasks/3

### ============== VALIDATION ERRORS ==============

### Missing title
POST http://localhost:3000/api/v1/tasks
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### Invalid priority
POST http://localhost:3000/api/v1/tasks
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Bad priority",
  "priority": "urgent"
}

### Invalid due date
POST http://localhost:3000/api/v1/tasks
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Bad date",
  "dueDate": "not-a-date"
}

### ============== REQUEST ID PROPAGATION ==============

### Send a custom request ID — should appear in response and logs
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/tasks
X-Request-ID: my-custom-trace-id-12345